				<input id="_5" type="checkbox">
				<div class="SIT"><br><ul><li>Inspection of the upstream region of the rtcA/rctB promoter did not identify obvious sequence repeats that could act as likely targets for RtcR .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=9738023" target="_blank">9738023</a>]<br></li>
